    Accept leading digits in hostnames as per RFC 1123.

    Signed-off-by: Edward Z. Yang <ezyang@cs.stanford.edu>
---
 NEWS                                        |  2 ++
 library/HTMLPurifier/AttrDef/URI/Host.php   | 16 +++++++++++-----
